name: Ski Robin Christmas Card
description:
2 colour screen-printed christmas card. 

Printed by hand using water-based inks on high quality recycled 'Oatmeal' card which has a subtle grey fleck texture.

name: Robo-knit
description:
Like robots, like knitting...? then this one's for you, just a fun image crafted with love !
 
Silkscreen Print, hand-printed by myself.

2 colour, water-based ink on 380micron white Quantock board.

Please be aware that as this image has been hand printed, there is likely to be some subtle variation between prints - this is all part of the charm of screen printing!

Size: A4, 297mm x 210mm

Edition: 8

Signed, titled, numbered & unframed

This print will be carefully packaged and shipped flat so it should arrive at your door in tip-top condition.
